OL,6,FBins are overflowing and rubbish is
OL,7,Fscattered across the streets of South
OL,8,FTyneside as industrial action
OL,9,Fcontinues.
OL,11,FSouth Tyneside Council launched an
OL,12,Findependent investigation into
OL,13,Fgrievances raised by refuse
OL,14,Foperatives, which the GMB union say
OL,15,Fincluded claims of bullying and
OL,16,Fmismanagement, in June. The
OL,17,Finvestigation into the claims
OL,18,Fconcluded in November 2023.
