OL,6,FThe strike - which means the next
OL,7,Fcollection is 26 January - follows
OL,8,Fprevious action in November, December
OL,9,Fand earlier this month.
OL,11,FThe unions are warning of more strikes
OL,12,Fin the coming months, over what they
OL,13,Fsay is an "accumulation of years of
OL,14,Fintolerable working conditions".
