OL,6,FThe unions have said new housing has
OL,7,Fincreased the workload of refuse
OL,8,Fcollections, without extra staff or
OL,9,Fbin lorries, and allege they have been
OL,10,Fserved disciplinary notices for
OL,11,Fhelping elderly people while
OL,12,Fcompleting their rounds.
