OL,6,FThe council told ITV News that the
OL,7,F"original collective grievance,
OL,8,Fsubmitted in June 2023, did not
OL,9,Finclude any allegations of bullying
OL,10,Fand mismanagement. The collective
OL,11,Fgrievance specifically cited finishing
OL,12,Fon time, size of rounds and said that
OL,13,Fit sought consistency in the way leave
OL,14,Fwas allocated."
