OL,6,FA GMB spokesman said: "GMB members are
OL,7,Fextremely disappointed that we have
OL,8,Fnot been given a copy of the
OL,9,Findependent report that we were
OL,10,Fpromised, instead we've been given a
OL,11,Fwhitewashed report written by the Head
OL,12,Fof Service, Stuart Wright, who in our
OL,13,Fview is biased and not impartial.
OL,15,F"We've also had no contact or offers
OL,16,Ffrom South Tyneside Council to meet to
OL,17,Fresolve the dispute so the action goes
OL,18,Fahead this week again.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
