OL,6,F"We have been told if we share the
OL,7,Freport with anyone they will deny us
OL,8,Fthe right to appeal against the
OL,9,Foutcomes of the Wright report.J"As the
OL,10,Faction we've taken seems not to have
OL,11,Ftriggered any response from management
OL,12,For the elected members of the ruling
OL,13,Fparty, we are now considering our next
OL,14,Fsteps and cannot rule out indefinite
OL,15,Faction being taken in the near future."
