OL,6,FThe council added that it had made
OL,7,Fclear to the unions "that if any of
OL,8,Fthe contents of that report were
OL,9,Fshared publicly, there was a potential
OL,10,Ffor the appeal process to be
OL,11,Fcompromised. The council thought that
OL,12,Fthis was well understood by all
OL,13,Fparties. The GMB's actions may put at
OL,14,Frisk the viability of any appeal
OL,15,Fprocess."
OL,17,FResidents are being advised to present
OL,18,Fboth their recycling and household bin
OL,19,Fon non-strike days when one will be
OL,20,Fcollected, which the council say will
OL,21,Fhelp to minimise disruption.
