OL,6,FThere have been more slots added at
OL,7,FMiddlefields Recycling Village,
OL,8,Fhowever as of Tuesday afternoon, the
OL,9,Ffirst available slot was on Monday 29
OL,10,FJanuary.
OL,12,FThe refuse service supports 72,000
OL,13,Fhouseholds across South Tyneside,
OL,14,Femptying 6.2 million bins every year.
OL,16,FA Unite spokesman said: "Unite will
OL,17,Fcontinue to support members who are
OL,18,Fseeking improved industrial relations,
OL,19,Fin this dispute with South Tyneside
OL,20,FCouncil."
